<h2>Booking Confirmation</h2>
<p>Dear <%= @user.email %>,</p>
<p>Your venue booking has been confirmed.</p>
<p>Here are your booking details:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Venue:</strong> <%= @venue.name %></li>
  <li><strong>Building:</strong> <%= @venue.building %></li>
  <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @venue_record.date %></li>
  <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @venue_record.time.strftime("%H:%M") %></li>
</ul>
<p>Thank you for your booking.</p>